TA-2003-06 php-form-misconfiguration in VisNetic WebMail v.5.8.6.6
contributed by: rushjo
=========================================================================
Tripbit Security Advisory

TA-2003-06 php-form-misconfiguration in VisNetic WebMail v.5.8.6.6
=========================================================================


PROGRAM: VisNetic WebMail v.5.8.6.6
HOMEPAGE: http://www.deerfield.com
VULNERABLE VERSIONS: v.5.8.6.6
RISK: Medium
IMPACT: Unauthorized file viewing
RELEASE DATE: 2003-06


